 "html": "<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6033 size-full\" src=\"/media/uploads/2020/08/Koljanderblomkoolrys.jpg\" alt width=\"2048\" height=\"1365\" srcset=\"/media/uploads/2020/08/Koljanderblomkoolrys.jpg 2048w, /media/uploads/2020/08/Koljanderblomkoolrys-600x400.jpg 600w, /media/uploads/2020/08/Koljanderblomkoolrys-300x200.jpg 300w, /media/uploads/2020/08/Koljanderblomkoolrys-1024x683.jpg 1024w, /media/uploads/2020/08/Koljanderblomkoolrys-768x512.jpg 768w, /media/uploads/2020/08/Koljanderblomkoolrys-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, /media/uploads/2020/08/Koljanderblomkoolrys-750x500.jpg 750w, /media/uploads/2020/08/Koljanderblomkoolrys-380x253.jpg 380w, /media/uploads/2020/08/Koljanderblomkoolrys-760x507.jpg 760w, /media/uploads/2020/08/Koljanderblomkoolrys-800x533.jpg 800w, /media/uploads/2020/08/Koljanderblomkoolrys-900x600.jpg 900w, /media/uploads/2020/08/Koljanderblomkoolrys-1800x1200.jpg 1800w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\"></p>\n<p><strong><u>KOLJANDER-BLOMKOOLRYS</u></strong></p>\n<p><strong><u> </u></strong></p>\n<p><strong><u>Bestanddele</u></strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>1 groot blomkool</li>\n<li>60 ml botter</li>\n<li>125 ml gesnipperde amandels</li>\n<li>10 ml suurlemoensap</li>\n<li>Sout en peper</li>\n<li>125 ml vars koljander</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong><u> </u></strong></p>\n<p><strong><u>Metode</u></strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Kap die blomkool fyn I die voedselverwerker</li>\n<li>Smelt die botter en braai die blomkool liggies daarin</li>\n<li>Voeg die suurlemoeonsap en sout en peper by en proe!</li>\n<li>Meng die amandels deur en roerbraai vir 1 minuut.</li>\n<li>Skep op en roer die fyn gekapte koljander deur</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong><u> </u></strong></p>\n<p><u> </u></p>",
